      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PHOENIX RED (5) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (22.46) at Warrnambool. Has a good record here at this journey. The form out of last race has been strong. Worth another chance. PAW HAZELDON (6) has a strong record here with three wins and four placings from nine starts. Was out of placings last time (23.67) at Warragul in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 12 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. PAW BAUTISTA (2) had won two in a row before finishing third (23.02) last time at Shepparton. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. Will give a great sight again. MISS COCO (1) cannot be ruled out.",
